    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You specify the value for this property using the unit coordinate space, where (",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "0",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ", ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "0",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ") is the bottom-left corner of the view’s ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/QuartzCore/CALayer/bounds",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " rectangle, and (",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "1",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ", ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "1",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ") is the top-right corner. The default value of this property is (",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "0.5",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ", ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "0.5",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": "), which represents the center of the view’s ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/QuartzCore/CALayer/bounds",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " rectangle.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "All geometric manipulations to the view occur about the specified point. For example, applying a rotation transform to a view with the default anchor point causes the view to rotate around its center. Changing the anchor point to a different location causes the view to rotate around that new point.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
